column6: [{'sContent': 'One of the products of this breakdown is the element chlorine.', 'sContent_eng': 'One of the products of this breakdown is the element chlorine.', 'sSpeech': 'One+of+the+products+of+this+breakdown+is+the+element+chlorine.&le=eng', 'sCn': '这种分解过程的产物之一是元素氯。'}, {'sContent': 'Direct and some metal composition chlorides of chlorine under the moist circumstance .', 'sContent_eng': 'Direct and some metal composition chlorides of chlorine under the moist circumstance .', 'sSpeech': 'Direct+and+some+metal+composition+chlorides+of+chlorine+under+the+moist+circumstance+.&le=eng', 'sCn': '氯在潮湿的情况下直接与某些金属合成氯化物。'}, {'sContent': '"But years of observation of geochemistry have taught me that caution is wise, " he says, "whether it be for the earlier claims on water or this latest work on chlorine isotopes.', 'sContent_eng': '"But years of observation of geochemistry have taught me that caution is wise, " he says, "whether it be for the earlier claims on water or this latest work on chlorine isotopes.', 'sSpeech': '%22But+years+of+observation+of+geochemistry+have+taught+me+that+caution+is+wise%2C+%22+he+says%2C+%22whether+it+be+for+the+earlier+claims+on+water+or+this+latest+work+on+chlorine+isotopes.&le=eng', 'sCn': '“但是，多年来对地球化学的观察让我知道谨慎是明智的，”他说，“无论是这次对于氯同位素的研究还是早期对于水的研究都需要谨慎。”'}]

column6: [{'sContent': 'But the brittleness of silicon limits its uses.', 'sContent_eng': 'But the brittleness of silicon limits its uses.', 'sSpeech': 'But+the+brittleness+of+silicon+limits+its+uses.&le=eng', 'sCn': '但是，硅的脆性也限制了其应用范围。'}, {'sContent': "They consist of silicon, sand and metal so there's no any connection to dinosaurs … Besides, we may see corrosion on some of them.", 'sContent_eng': "They consist of silicon, sand and metal so there's no any connection to dinosaurs … Besides, we may see corrosion on some of them.", 'sSpeech': 'They+consist+of+silicon%2C+sand+and+metal+so+there%27s+no+any+connection+to+dinosaurs+%E2%80%A6+Besides%2C+we+may+see+corrosion+on+some+of+them.&le=eng', 'sCn': '它们是由硅砂和金属构成的，和恐龙蛋没有任何关系……除此之外，我们还能看到它们上面的腐蚀的部分。'}, {'sContent': 'Because silicon, the main component of semiconductors, breaks down at about 200 degrees Fahrenheit , some experts believe a new material will be needed in a decade or so.', 'sContent_eng': 'Because silicon, the main component of semiconductors, breaks down at about 200 degrees Fahrenheit , some experts believe a new material will be needed in a decade or so.', 'sSpeech': 'Because+silicon%2C+the+main+component+of+semiconductors%2C+breaks+down+at+about+200+degrees+Fahrenheit+%2C+some+experts+believe+a+new+material+will+be+needed+in+a+decade+or+so.&le=eng', 'sCn': '因为半导体的主要成分硅在大约华氏200度就会破裂。 一些专家认为大约十年后将需要一种新的材料。'}]

column6: [{'sContent': 'Beryl is a beryllium-aluminum silicate, and its color comes from small amounts of chromium.', 'sContent_eng': 'Beryl is a beryllium-aluminum silicate, and its color comes from small amounts of chromium.', 'sSpeech': 'Beryl+is+a+beryllium-aluminum+silicate%2C+and+its+color+comes+from+small+amounts+of+chromium.&le=eng', 'sCn': '绿宝石其实是一种铍铝硅酸盐，而它的颜色则来自于微量的铬元素。'}, {'sContent': "This artist's concept illustrates how silicate crystals like those found in comets can be created by an outburst from a growing star.", 'sContent_eng': "This artist's concept illustrates how silicate crystals like those found in comets can be created by an outburst from a growing star.", 'sSpeech': 'This+artist%27s+concept+illustrates+how+silicate+crystals+like+those+found+in+comets+can+be+created+by+an+outburst+from+a+growing+star.&le=eng', 'sCn': '这幅艺术构想图说明了在彗星中发现的硅酸盐晶体是如何在生长中的恒星的喷发中生成的。'}, {'sContent': 'One question that has baffled planetary scientists is how oceans formed on the surface of terrestrial planets like Earth -- rocky planets made of silicate and metals.', 'sContent_eng': 'One question that has baffled planetary scientists is how oceans formed on the surface of terrestrial planets like Earth -- rocky planets made of silicate and metals.', 'sSpeech': 'One+question+that+has+baffled+planetary+scientists+is+how+oceans+formed+on+the+surface+of+terrestrial+planets+like+Earth+--+rocky+planets+made+of+silicate+and+metals.&le=eng', 'sCn': '一个困扰着行星科学家的问题是：海洋是怎样在像地球这样由硅酸盐和金属组成的石质行星的表面形成的？'}]

column6: [{'sContent': 'In theory, psychoanalysis is the philosophy of the unconscious mind; in practice it is a means by which mental disorders can be cured.', 'sContent_eng': 'In theory, psychoanalysis is the philosophy of the unconscious mind; in practice it is a means by which mental disorders can be cured.', 'sSpeech': 'In+theory%2C+psychoanalysis+is+the+philosophy+of+the+unconscious+mind%3B+in+practice+it+is+a+means+by+which+mental+disorders+can+be+cured.&le=eng', 'sCn': '在理论上，精神分析是一门关于无意识心理的哲学；在实践上，它又是一种治愈心理紊乱的方法。'}, {'sContent': 'ASK someone to name a famous psychologist, and chances are they will pick Sigmund Freud (pictured), the bearded Austrian academic who came up with the idea of psychoanalysis.', 'sContent_eng': 'ASK someone to name a famous psychologist, and chances are they will pick Sigmund Freud (pictured), the bearded Austrian academic who came up with the idea of psychoanalysis.', 'sSpeech': 'ASK+someone+to+name+a+famous+psychologist%2C+and+chances+are+they+will+pick+Sigmund+Freud+%28pictured%29%2C+the+bearded+Austrian+academic+who+came+up+with+the+idea+of+psychoanalysis.&le=eng', 'sCn': '说起著名的心理学家，人们可能会想到西格蒙德弗洛伊德（如图），这位满脸大胡子的奥地利学者提出了精神分析的概念。'}, {'sContent': 'For the woman, her love can turn a frog into a beautiful man, while for the man love reduces the woman to what psychoanalysis calls a "partial object", that in you which makes me desire you.', 'sContent_eng': 'For the woman, her love can turn a frog into a beautiful man, while for the man love reduces the woman to what psychoanalysis calls a "partial object", that in you which makes me desire you.', 'sSpeech': 'For+the+woman%2C+her+love+can+turn+a+frog+into+a+beautiful+man%2C+while+for+the+man+love+reduces+the+woman+to+what+psychoanalysis+calls+a+%22partial+object%22%2C+that+in+you+which+makes+me+desire+you.&le=eng', 'sCn': '对女人而言，她的爱可以让一只青蛙变成一位英俊的男性，而对男人来说，他的爱则把女人降低为了精神分析所谓的“部分客体”，在你身上使我欲望你的东西。'}]

column6: [{'sContent': 'And in the other room another chimpanzee is placed.', 'sContent_eng': 'And in the other room another chimpanzee is placed.', 'sSpeech': 'And+in+the+other+room+another+chimpanzee+is+placed.&le=eng', 'sCn': '而在那个房间里有另一只黑猩猩。'}, {'sContent': 'In chimpanzee groups, females mate with all the males, in what appears to be a strategy to reduce the risk of her children being killed by older males.', 'sContent_eng': 'In chimpanzee groups, females mate with all the males, in what appears to be a strategy to reduce the risk of her children being killed by older males.', 'sSpeech': 'In+chimpanzee+groups%2C+females+mate+with+all+the+males%2C+in+what+appears+to+be+a+strategy+to+reduce+the+risk+of+her+children+being+killed+by+older+males.&le=eng', 'sCn': '在黑猩猩群体中，雌性和所有雄性交配，这种策略是为了降低自己的孩子被更年长雄性杀死的风险。'}, {'sContent': 'Rather, we may have such strong feeling of morality because, without them, we would revert to the "evil" behavior inherent in the 97.3 percent of us that is chimpanzee.', 'sContent_eng': 'Rather, we may have such strong feeling of morality because, without them, we would revert to the "evil" behavior inherent in the 97.3 percent of us that is chimpanzee.', 'sSpeech': 'Rather%2C+we+may+have+such+strong+feeling+of+morality+because%2C+without+them%2C+we+would+revert+to+the+%22evil%22+behavior+inherent+in+the+97.3+percent+of+us+that+is+chimpanzee.&le=eng', 'sCn': '而应该说，我们拥有强烈的道德意识感是因为，没了它们，我们会向体内97.3%的基因中先天“恶行”部分倾斜而堕落成黑猩猩。'}]

column6: [{'sContent': 'With a few exceptions, the technique for building a skyscraper is similar whether you are in Europe or you are in Singapore.', 'sContent_eng': 'With a few exceptions, the technique for building a skyscraper is similar whether you are in Europe or you are in Singapore.', 'sSpeech': 'With+a+few+exceptions%2C+the+technique+for+building+a+skyscraper+is+similar+whether+you+are+in+Europe+or+you+are+in+Singapore.&le=eng', 'sCn': '除了少数特例外，不管是在欧洲还是新加坡，建造一幢摩天楼的技术大体上是相似的。'}, {'sContent': 'He talks of building a "digital skyscraper, " a company whose services are so indispensable that someday we will look back and wonder how we managed to do without it.', 'sContent_eng': 'He talks of building a "digital skyscraper, " a company whose services are so indispensable that someday we will look back and wonder how we managed to do without it.', 'sSpeech': 'He+talks+of+building+a+%22digital+skyscraper%2C+%22+a+company+whose+services+are+so+indispensable+that+someday+we+will+look+back+and+wonder+how+we+managed+to+do+without+it.&le=eng', 'sCn': '他谈到要建立一座“数字摩天楼”，其服务是如此不可或缺，以至于会有那么一天，我们将怀疑没有它到底还能做什么。'}, {'sContent': '"However, given high costs of building skyscrapers and maintaining them as well as environmental problems they cause, government should be cautious in approving skyscraper projects, " he said.', 'sContent_eng': '"However, given high costs of building skyscrapers and maintaining them as well as environmental problems they cause, government should be cautious in approving skyscraper projects, " he said.', 'sSpeech': '%22However%2C+given+high+costs+of+building+skyscrapers+and+maintaining+them+as+well+as+environmental+problems+they+cause%2C+government+should+be+cautious+in+approving+skyscraper+projects%2C+%22+he+said.&le=eng', 'sCn': '然而，考虑到摩天楼的高造价和高维护费用，以及由此引起的环境问题，政府应谨慎批准摩天楼项目。'}]

column6: [{'sContent': 'Suddenly I saw a young male ruby-throated hummingbird in what had been a patch of flowering tobacco.', 'sContent_eng': 'Suddenly I saw a young male ruby-throated hummingbird in what had been a patch of flowering tobacco.', 'sSpeech': 'Suddenly+I+saw+a+young+male+ruby-throated+hummingbird+in+what+had+been+a+patch+of+flowering+tobacco.&le=eng', 'sCn': '突然，在一块种过烟草花的地里，我看见一只颈部深红色的幼小雄蜂鸟。'}, {'sContent': "Implanted sensors show that a hummingbird's wing flaps so fast that the brain is generating the muscle signal for the downbeat of its wing while the wing is still going up.", 'sContent_eng': "Implanted sensors show that a hummingbird's wing flaps so fast that the brain is generating the muscle signal for the downbeat of its wing while the wing is still going up.", 'sSpeech': 'Implanted+sensors+show+that+a+hummingbird%27s+wing+flaps+so+fast+that+the+brain+is+generating+the+muscle+signal+for+the+downbeat+of+its+wing+while+the+wing+is+still+going+up.&le=eng', 'sCn': '植入的传感器表明，蜂鸟翅膀击打的速度如此之快，以至于当其脑部发出的肌肉信号命令翅膀向下挥动时，但翅膀还是向上挥。'}, {'sContent': 'I can preserve his inspiring legacy more powerfully through writing than through the hummingbird pendant I wear around my neck to honor his homeland of Trinidad, or a picture or heirloom.', 'sContent_eng': 'I can preserve his inspiring legacy more powerfully through writing than through the hummingbird pendant I wear around my neck to honor his homeland of Trinidad, or a picture or heirloom.', 'sSpeech': 'I+can+preserve+his+inspiring+legacy+more+powerfully+through+writing+than+through+the+hummingbird+pendant+I+wear+around+my+neck+to+honor+his+homeland+of+Trinidad%2C+or+a+picture+or+heirloom.&le=eng', 'sCn': '比起我脖子上佩戴的那个纪念他的故乡特立尼达的蜂鸟链坠，或者一张照片，一个传家宝，写作可以让我更得宜有力地继承他那些激动人心的遗产。'}]
